product_name: DeLorme Wisconsin Atlas and Gazetteer - 12th Edition
long_description: The 12th edition DeLorme Wisconsin Atlas and Gazetteer offers detailed map coverage and information on the Badger State, from the Great Lakes to the Western Uplands. Includes 78 pages of shaded-relief maps with unequaled backroad detail for the entire state, with an additional 18 pages of gazetteer information. GPS-compatible maps contain Lat./Lon. tick marks and grid lines using the standard WGS84 datum. Map scale is 1:160,000. DeLorme Publishing; copyright 2011.
